/qqvoice>\"\n3. 支持格式: .silk, .slk, .slac, .amr, .wav, .mp3, .ogg, .pcm\n4. ⚠️ <qqvoice> 只用于语音文件，图片请用 <qqimg>；两者不要混用\n5. 可以同时发送文字和语音，系统会按顺序投递\n6. ⚠️ 插件 TTS 未配置: 如果你有 TTS 工具（如 audio_speech），仍可用它生成音频文件后用 <qqvoice> 发送；若无 TTS 工具，则无法主动生成语音\n7. 语音识别未配置（STT），无法自动转录用户的语音消息\n\n【发送文件 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发文件方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqfile>文件路径或URL</qqfile>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"这是你要的文档 <qqfile>/tmp/report.pdf</qqfile>\"\n3. 支持: 本地文件路径、公网 URL\n4. 适用于非图片非语音的文件（如 pdf, docx, xlsx, zip, txt 等）\n5. ⚠️ 图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，其他文件用 <qqfile>\n\n【发送视频 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发视频方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqvideo>路径或URL</qqvideo>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"<qqvideo>https://example.com/video.mp4</qqvideo>\" 或 \"<qqvideo>/path/to/video.mp4</qqvideo>\"\n3. 支持: 公网 URL、本地文件路径（系统自动读取上传）\n4. ⚠️ 视频用 <qqvideo>，图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，文件用 <qqfile>\n\n生成ppt"}],"timestamp":1773881602978}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0a95984","parentId":"ed3a0d89","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:53:27.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要根据刚才那张打印机的分类思维导图生成PPT。我需要：\n\n1. 创建一个PPT文件，包含打印机的分类信息\n2. 可以使用Python的python-pptx库来生成PPT\n3. 结构应该按照思维导图的逻辑来组织\n\n让我先检查是否安装了python-pptx，然后创建一个结构清晰的PPT。\n\nPPT结构：\n- 封面：打印机分类\n- 目录页：四大分类\n- 各分类详细页（可能需要多页）\n- 总结页","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dcc7afd6ea5f4fb7af8685bc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pip show python-pptx"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":2315,"output":230,"cacheRead":26037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28582,"cost":{"input":0.001389,"output":0.000506,"cacheRead":0.0028640700000000002,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004759070000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773881602980}}
{"type":"message","id":"e440d295","parentId":"a0a95984","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:53:30.690Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dcc7afd6ea5f4fb7af8685bc","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Name: python-pptx\r\nVersion: 1.0.2\r\nSummary: Create, read, and update PowerPoint 2007+ (.pptx) files.\r\nHome-page: \r\nAuthor: \r\nAuthor-email: Steve Canny <stcanny@gmail.com>\r\nLicense: MIT\r\nLocation: C:\\Program Files\\Python312\\Lib\\site-packages\r\nRequires: lxml, Pillow, typing-extensions, XlsxWriter\r\nRequired-by:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3436,"aggregated":"Name: python-pptx\r\nVersion: 1.0.2\r\nSummary: Create, read, and update PowerPoint 2007+ (.pptx) files.\r\nHome-page: \r\nAuthor: \r\nAuthor-email: Steve Canny <stcanny@gmail.com>\r\nLicense: MIT\r\nLocation: C:\\Program Files\\Python312\\Lib\\site-packages\r\nRequires: lxml, Pillow, typing-extensions, XlsxWriter\r\nRequired-by:","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773881610687}}
{"type":"message","id":"b91e20e9","parentId":"e440d295","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:54:03.030Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，python-pptx已经安装了。现在我需要创建一个Python脚本来生成PPT。让我创建一个结构清晰的PPT。\n\nPPT结构：\n1. 封面页：打印机分类体系\n2. 目录页：四大分类概览\n3. 标签打印机（2页：便携+台式）\n4. 工业条码打印机（1页）\n5. 家用办公打印机（1页）\n6. 票据打印机（1页）\n7. 总结页\n\n让我创建一个Python脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_47526526d9f54406972d26c4","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\create_printer_ppt.py","content":"from pptx import Presentation\nfrom pptx.util import Inches, Pt\nfrom pptx.dml.color import RGBColor\nfrom pptx.enum.text import PP_ALIGN, MSO_ANCHOR\n\ndef create_printer_ppt():\n    prs = Presentation()\n\n    # 设置幻灯片尺寸为16:9\n    prs.slide_width = Inches(13.333)\n    prs.slide_height = Inches(7.5)\n\n    def add_title_slide(title, subtitle=\"\"):\n        \"\"\"添加标题页\"\"\"\n        slide_layout = prs.slide_layouts[0]  # 标题页\n        slide = prs.slides.add_slide(slide_layout)\n        slide.shapes.title.text = title\n        if subtitle:\n            slide.placeholders[1].text = subtitle\n        return slide\n\n    def add_content_slide(title, contents):\n        \"\"\"添加内容页\"\"\"\n        slide_layout = prs.slide_layouts[5]  # 空白页\n        slide = prs.slides.add_slide(slide_layout)\n\n        # 添加标题\n        left = Inches(0.5)\n        top = Inches(0.3)\n        width = Inches(12.333)\n        height = Inches(1)\n        title_box = slide.shapes.add_textbox(left, top, width, height)\n        title_frame = title_box.text_frame\n        title_para = title_frame.paragraphs[0]\n        title_para.text = title\n        title_para.font.size = Pt(32)\n        title_para.font.bold = True\n        title_para.font.color.rgb = RGBColor(0, 51, 102)  # 深蓝色\n\n        # 添加内容\n        left = Inches(0.5)\n        top = Inches(1.5)\n        width = Inches(12.333)\n        height = Inches(5.5)\n        content_box = slide.shapes.add_textbox(left, top, width, height)\n        content_frame = content_box.text_frame\n        content_frame.word_wrap = True\n\n        for i, content in enumerate(contents):\n            if i == 0:\n                p = content_frame.paragraphs[0]\n            else:\n                p = content_frame.add_paragraph()\n\n            p.text = content\n            p.font.size = Pt(18)\n            p.space_after = Pt(12)\n            p.font.color.rgb = RGBColor(51, 51, 51)  # 深灰色\n\n            if content.startswith(\"●\") or content.startswith(\"•\") or content.startswith(\"○\"):\n                p.level = 0\n                p.font.bold = True\n            elif content.startswith(\"  -\"):\n                p.level = 1\n                p.font.bold = False\n            elif content.startswith(\"    -\"):\n                p.level = 2\n                p.font.bold = False\n\n        return slide\n\n    # 1. 封面\n    add_title_slide(\"打印机分类体系\", \"按应用场景与规格分类\")\n\n    # 2. 目录\n    add_content_slide(\"四大分类\", [\n        \"● 标签打印机\",\n        \"  - 便携式打印机\",\n        \"  - 台式打印机\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 工业条码打印机\",\n        \"  - 工业4寸热转印\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 家用办公打印机\",\n        \"  - 半寸、2寸、8寸\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 票据打印机\",\n        \"  - 58mm、80mm（高速160mm/s以上）\"\n    ])\n\n    # 3. 标签打印机 - 便携\n    add_content_slide(\"标签打印机 - 便携系列\", [\n        \"● 半寸热转印打印机\",\n        \"  - 应用场景：丝带、线号等标识\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 2寸便携打印机\",\n        \"  - 应用场景：小价签、分类标签\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 3寸便携打印机\",\n        \"  - 应用场景：\",\n        \"    - 商超价签、食品标签\",\n        \"    - 货架条码、商品条码\",\n        \"    - 快递一联单、小外箱标签\",\n        \"    - 入库标签\"\n    ])\n\n    # 4. 标签打印机 - 台式\n    add_content_slide(\"标签打印机 - 台式系列\", [\n        \"● 2.5寸台式打印机\",\n        \"  - 应用场景：奶茶、鞋服、烘焙价签、医疗景区腕带等\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 3寸台式打印机\",\n        \"  - 应用场景：茶饮、烘焙、商超、生鲜行业\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 4寸台式打印机\",\n        \"  - 应用场景：快递仓储面单\"\n    ])\n\n    # 5. 工业条码打印机\n    add_content_slide(\"工业条码打印机\", [\n        \"● 工业4寸热转印打印机\",\n        \"\",\n        \"核心技术特点：\",\n        \"  - 热转印技术，打印质量高\",\n        \"  - 可打印条码、二维码\",\n        \"  - 工业级耐用性\",\n        \"\",\n        \"主要应用场景：\",\n        \"  - 工业条码打印\",\n        \"  - 产品流水标贴\",\n        \"  - 仓储物流标签\",\n        \"  - 批量生产标识\"\n    ])\n\n    # 6. 家用办公打印机\n    add_content_slide(\"家用办公打印机\", [\n        \"● 半寸打印机\",\n        \"  - 应用：收纳、分类、标识\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 2寸打印机\",\n        \"  - AI打印机：语音转图片\",\n        \"  - 家用标签、错题机、收纳、手帐\",\n        \"  - 儿童拍立得\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 8寸打印机\",\n        \"  - 文档：A4办公文档、作业\",\n        \"  - 文身：文身工作室、贴纸\"\n    ])\n\n    # 7. 票据打印机\n    add_content_slide(\"票据打印机（高速160mm/s以上）\", [\n        \"● 58mm票据打印机\",\n        \"  - 国内市场：商超、外卖\",\n        \"  - 东南亚市场：商超、外卖\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 80mm票据打印机（带切刀）\",\n        \"  - 欧美市场：商超、零售\",\n        \"\",\n        \"技术特点：\",\n        \"  - 高速打印：160mm/s以上\",\n        \"  - 自动切刀功能\",\n        \"  - 适用于高频打印场景\"\n    ])\n\n    # 8. 总结\n    add_content_slide(\"总结\", [\n        \"● 打印机按应用场景可分为四大类：\",\n        \"  - 标签打印机：便携+台式，涵盖半寸到4寸\",\n        \"  - 工业条码打印机：工业4寸热转印，专业化生产\",\n        \"  - 家用办公打印机：半寸到8寸，满足多样化需求\",\n        \"  - 票据打印机：58mm/80mm，高速打印\",\n        \"\",\n        \"● 选型建议：\",\n        \"  - 根据打印尺寸、打印量、应用场景选择\",\n        \"  - 标签类看便携性/台式需求\",\n        \"  - 工业类看耐用性和打印质量\",\n        \"  - 家用类看功能多样性和易用性\"\n    ])\n\n    # 保存\n    output_path = r\"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\打印机分类体系.pptx\"\n    prs.save(output_path)\n    print(f\"PPT已生成：{output_path}\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    create_printer_ppt()\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":97,"output":1875,"cacheRead":28473,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30445,"cost":{"input":0.0000582,"output":0.004125,"cacheRead":0.00313203,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00731523}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773881610691}}
